<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥ -<span class="c5"> قوله تعالى:</span> امْرَأَتَ نُوحٍ <span class="c4">[التحريم: ١٠]</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٦ -<span class="c5"> قوله تعالى:</span> وَامْرَأَتَ لُوطٍ <span class="c4">[التحريم: ١٠]</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٧ -<span class="c5"> قوله تعالى:</span> امْرَأَتَ فِرْعَوْنَ* <span class="c4">[التحريم: ١١]</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
